dct_title_s: North Sea, United Kingdom--Netherlands, Orford Ness to Cromer and Rotterdam to Terschelling (Raster Image)
dct_description_sm: Prepared and published by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. "Copyright 2008 by the United States Government. No copyright claimed on Title 17 U.S.C." "Soundings in meters." Includes index to next larger scale charts, and source diagram. Georeferenced nautical chart. Map no. 37166.
This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
This layer is presented in the WGS84 coordinate system for web display purposes. Downloadable data are provided in native coordinate system or projection.
